# FitWear â€“ A React E-Commerce App

FitWear is a fully functional and styled e-commerce web application built using **React**. It supports browsing fashion products, liking items, searching through listings, cart and checkout flow, dark/light theme, and route protection with login/signup.

---

## Features

- Product listing with dynamic data
- Like toggle for each product (using `useState`)
- Search filter using controlled input
- Light/Dark Theme Toggle (via `useContext`)
- Protected checkout page for logged-in users
- Login & Sign-Up functionality
- Cart system with real-time item count
- Checkout page with full billing breakdown (GST, discounts, delivery)
- Responsive UI with custom styling
